EN: I just received a package from the courier.
ZH: 今天没有快递送到。
EN: There were no deliveries today.
ZH: 我将快递送到你的家里。
EN: I will deliver the package to your home.
ZH: 这是一个急需快递的文件。
EN: This is an urgent document that needs to be delivered.
ZH: 请确认你的收件地址，以便我们能发出快递。
EN: Please confirm your shipping address so that we can send the package.
ZH: 快递通常需要几天的时间送达。
EN: Deliveries usually take several days to arrive.
ZH: 我们会为你提供快递追踪号码。
EN: We will provide you with a tracking number for the package.
ZH: 请签收这份快递。
EN: Please sign for this delivery.
ZH: 快递费用将会在结算时添加到账单上。
EN: The delivery fee will be added to your invoice during checkout.
ZH: 我们接受信用卡和支付宝支付快递费用。
EN: We accept credit card and Alipay payments for delivery charges.
ZH: 这个快递包裹签收后如有疑问，请及时联系客服。
EN: If you have any questions about this package after you sign for it, please contact customer service immediately.
ZH: 快递员将于明天早上10点到达你的住址。
EN: The courier will arrive at your address tomorrow morning at 10 o'clock.
ZH: 请准备好身份证明来领取快递。
EN: Please have your identification ready to collect the package.
ZH: 这个快递包裹比较重，请帮我一起搬上楼。
EN: This package is quite heavy, can you help me carry it upstairs?
ZH: 如果你不在家，快递员会把包裹放在你家门口。
EN: If you're not at home, the courier will leave the package at your doorstep.
ZH: 我发现这个快递包裹反封条被打开了。
EN: I noticed that the seal on this package has been opened.
ZH: 应该有人替换了我期待的快递。
EN: Someone must have replaced the delivery I was expecting.
ZH: 你可以在网上预约快递上门取件。
EN: You can schedule a courier pickup online.
ZH: 我用手机下单购买了一份快递。
EN: I placed an order for a package using my smartphone.
ZH: 我把快递包裹放在邮箱里了。
EN: I left the package in the mailbox.
